---
name: scaffold_page
description: Generate a new Flutter page (widget + route) with Fly conventions
input:
  schema:
    name:
      type: string
      required: true
      description: The name of the page to scaffold
    stateManagement:
      type: string
      required: false
      default: riverpod
      description: State management approach (default: riverpod)
---
Create a Flutter page named "{{name}}" using {{stateManagement}}. Include a widget, route, and basic tests.

